room_title: Escape room "The Doorman" by Eerie Escape in Columbus
room_description:
As new investigative reporters, you have been “volun-TOLD” to take on a stale case. The case involves a doorman that is suspected of stealing valuable items from people staying in his building. You have tracked the location of his parlor -  where the valuable items are being kept.
​Little do you know, he is aware that you are on to his thievery and he welcomes you to walk into his trap.  You will soon find out that theft is not his only crime. Will you be able to find the clues to escape or will you become the next headline?
